{"title":"Downscaling","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Downscaling","toc":true},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div style=\"max-width:960px;margin:2rem auto;padding:0 1.5rem;\">\n\n  <span class=\"section-label\">Metodología y resultados</span>\n  <h2 style=\"color:#003087;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">Downscaling estadístico</h2>\n  <p style=\"color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">\n    El algoritmo de análogos sinópticos proporciona precipitación diaria en una malla de 5×5 km (20.945 celdas) sobre la Península Ibérica e Islas Baleares, a partir de datos de baja resolución de los modelos de predicción estacional.\n  </p>\n\n  <!-- Descripción metodológica -->\n  <div class=\"grid-2\" style=\"margin-bottom:2rem;\">\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 1 · Calibración</h3>\n      <p>Clasificación de tipos de tiempo mediante <em>K-means clustering</em> para identificar la base de datos sinóptica de referencia (1981–1996). La similitud se calcula a partir de distancias euclídeas ponderadas de las componentes del viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa (ERA5).</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"info-card\">\n      <h3>Fase 2 · Estimación</h3>\n      <p>La precipitación para cada celda se estima como la media ponderada de la precipitación asociada a las situaciones más análogas de la base de referencia, usando la similitud de los campos de viento geostrófico en superficie y a 500 hPa de los modelos C3S.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <!-- DESPLEGABLES POR MODELO                                       -->\n  <!-- ============================================================ -->\n  <h3 style=\"color:#003087;margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Resultados por modelo</h3>\n  <p style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Período de validez: <strong>AMJ 2026</strong> · Lead: marzo 2026</p>\n\n  <div class=\"accordion\" id=\"accordion-modelos\">\n\n    <!-- ECMWF -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-ecmwf\">\n          ECMWF-SEAS5.1\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-ecmwf\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles ECMWF\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación ECMWF\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC ECMWF\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS ECMWF\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS) · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_ecmwf_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS ECMWF\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- DWD -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-dwd\">\n          DWD\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-dwd\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles DWD\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación DWD\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC DWD\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS DWD\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS) · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_dwd_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS DWD\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- CMCC -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-cmcc\">\n          CMCC\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-cmcc\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles CMCC\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/4_corr-spearman_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Correlación CMCC\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Correlación de Spearman · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/5_roc_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"ROC CMCC\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Curvas ROC · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/6_rps_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"RPS CMCC\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Ranked Probability Score (RPS) · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/7_bs_3_pr_cmcc_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"BS CMCC\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Brier Score · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Météo-France -->\n    <div class=\"accordion-item\">\n      <h2 class=\"accordion-header\">\n        <button class=\"accordion-button collapsed\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#mod-mf\">\n          Météo-France\n        </button>\n      </h2>\n      <div id=\"mod-mf\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion-modelos\">\n        <div class=\"accordion-body\">\n          <div class=\"grid-2\">\n            <div>\n              <img src=\"images/downscaling/3_terciles_meteo_france_lead032026_AMJ.png\" class=\"result-img\" alt=\"Terciles Météo-France\"/>\n              <p class=\"img-caption\">Probabilidad por terciles · Precipitación · AMJ 2026</p>\n            </div>\n            <div